CCP certified","text":"<p>Made in HAACP certified factory to ensure the highest quality standards.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_zC8qxQ","text_4DENA4","text_pwK4yV"],"settings":{"alignment":"center","mobile_alignment":"center","columns":3,"icons_width":80,"heading":"","subheading":"","bg_color":"","text_color":"#333333","box_color":"","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--medium","enable_slider_mobile":false,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"overlapping-images-0":{"type":"section-overlapping-images","settings":{"text_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","images_width":750,"images_offset":60,"image_link_1":"","image_link_2":"","hide_image_2":false,"title":"<p>Fall asleep and sleep <em>well<\/em><\/p>","heading_highlight_type":"highlight","highlight_color":"#0a2240","highlight_text_color":"#ffffff","description":"<p>Not all calories are created equal; the quality of the food you consume matters significantly. This principle applies to sleep as well. Therefore, our aim is to not only help you in the process of falling asleep but more importantly, to enhance the quality of sleep.<\/p><p>We not only focus on the short term effects, also the long term effects. Ashwagandha improves blood flow to the brain, thereby boosting oxygen and nutrient delivery. L-Theanine promotes mental relaxation by stimulating alfa waves, aiding in stress management without causing drowsiness. Over time, the combined effects of these substances could significantly support brain health, cognitive abilities, and overall mental well-being.<\/p>","heading_size":100,"button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--small","video_text":"","video_link":"","bg_color_secondary":false,"gradient":"","animation":"horizontal","animation_intensity":50,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"section_text_i9DFxi":{"type":"section-text","blocks":{"heading_wnCUzy":{"type":"heading","settings":{"text":"<p>Ingredients:<\/p>","size":100,"heading_highlight_type":"italics","highlight_color":"#d43747","highlight_text_color":"#000000"}},"text_QWVhmt":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>BKM supplements are formulated with a variety of ingredients, each chosen for their specific bioactive properties that address different biological needs in the human body. All BKM supplements are created in Sweden.<\/p>","size":100}}},"block_order":["heading_wnCUzy","text_QWVhmt"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"text_position":"center","bg_color_secondary":false,"text_color":"text-dark","width":"wrapper--narrow","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"section_image_BXhgzY":{"type":"section-image","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Frame_40_5e5a8796-a84b-4e3e-9e62-e9bd2da6043b.png","height":"original-height","enable_mobile_height":false,"mobile_height":"original-height-mobile","enable_stretch":true,"image_position":"center","bg_color_secondary":false,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":40}},"38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311":{"type":"section-columns","blocks":{"template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-0":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/li-meditation.jpg","title":"1. Before sleep","text":"<p>Initially, the natural ingredients will reduce your cortisol and stress levels, making you feel more relaxed and facilitating a smoother transition into a state of calm.<\/p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--text","button_size":"btn--small","video_link_popup":"","video_link_color":"text-dark"}},"template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-1":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"2. Falling asleep","text":"<p>Higher cortisol and stress levels is often the reason we “sit up and think” without being able to sleep, so by lowering these levels you will be able to fall asleep quicker and easier.<\/p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--text","button_size":"btn--small","video_link_popup":"","video_link_color":"text-dark"}},"template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-2":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"3. During sleep","text":"<p>The magnesium is essential for the body to be able to fall into REM sleep, the sleep that makes you energised.<\/p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--text","button_size":"btn--small","video_link_popup":"","video_link_color":"text-dark"}},"text_block_xWKCCm":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"4. Long Term effects","text":"<p>Ashwagandha improves blood flow to the brain, L-Theanine promotes mental relaxation, aiding in stress management without causing drowsiness. Summarized, this support brain health, cognitive abilities, and overall mental well-being.<\/p>","button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--text","button_size":"btn--small","video_link_popup":"","video_link_color":"text-dark"}}},"block_order":["template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-0","template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-1","template--18952594129217__38ff978b-66eb-4318-9ce0-94db8ff86311-1683126238ada0cf52-2","text_block_xWKCCm"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"What happens in your body?","align_text":"text-left","columns":3,"show_images":true,"show_borders":false,"equalize_height":true,"desktop_aspect_ratio":0.9,"mobile_aspect_ratio":0.9,"heading_size":120,"text_size":100,"bg_color_secondary":false,"color_borders":"#000000","layout_mobile":"carousel","width":"wrapper","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"section_overlapping_images_jANHAF":{"type":"section-overlapping-images","settings":{"text_position":"left","text_alignment":"left","images_width":750,"images_offset":60,"image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2024-02-28_at_14.56_1.png","image_link_1":"","image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Photo_2023-07-26_13_50_27.jpg","image_link_2":"","hide_image_2":false,"title":"<p>Created by Li, Swedish champion in free diving<\/p>","heading_highlight_type":"circle","highlight_color":"#d43747","highlight_text_color":"#000000","description":"<p>Li Karlsén, the Swedish freediver, once aimed for the skies but fate anchored her to the ground. After a tragic accident, she not only recovered but excelled, diving deep into the ocean's embrace. Her journey took her from seeking adversaries in Afghanistan to the tranquil depths of the sea.<\/p>","heading_size":100,"button_text":"","button_link":"","button_color":"btn--black","button_style":"btn--solid","button_size":"btn--small","video_text":"","video_link":"","bg_color_secondary":false,"gradient":"","animation":"horizontal","animation_intensity":50,"width":"wrapper--full-padded","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"171863460703bb35e0":{"type":"apps","settings":{"bg_color":"","width":"wrapper","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"17460068844ea5e81f":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"klaviyo_reviews_product_reviews_GDHHVn":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/klaviyo-reviews\/blocks\/product-reviews\/db20e365-d984-4ac4-9655-e1588d951ca9","settings":{}}},"block_order":["klaviyo_reviews_product_reviews_GDHHVn"],"settings":{"bg_color":"","width":"wrapper","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"tabs":{"type":"section-accordions","blocks":{"acordion-0":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Can I split the capsule?","text":"<p>Yes, you can split the capsule.  Simply open the capsule and mix the contents with your preferred food or beverage.<\/p>"}},"acordion-2":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Heading","text":"<p>Use this text block to discuss some commonly asked questions like shipping and returns, sizing, warranties, or product and company details.<\/p>"}},"d0